  "remarks": "Former judge of the Supreme Economic Court, Councellor in the Court of the Eurasian Economic Community (since 19 November 2012). He sustained the ban of the independent «Autoradio» station on 29 March 2011. The radio station had been transmitting the electoral programme of Mr. Sannikov, one of the opposition candidates in the Presidential election of December 2010.",
